## Conclusion

The AEGIS eBPF agent provides a complete backend-integrated solution for real-time network policy enforcement using kernel-space eBPF programs. The system offers:

- **Real-time enforcement** via eBPF programs
- **Dynamic policy updates** through BPF maps
- **Comprehensive telemetry** for observability
- **RESTful API** for backend integration
- **High performance** kernel-level processing
- **Production-ready** security and monitoring

This architecture enables centralized policy management with distributed, high-performance enforcement at the host level.
